Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了？嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  由由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上越发地冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真不想从被窝里出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘  还没有好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐  早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  由乃你们也在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}{\an8}{\fs27}「2月6日  樱花樱花」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是情人节了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生们已经决定好要送巧克力的人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师我的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘…密…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才沙英学姐怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好像不太平静的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8F8F8F&}{\3c&FFFFFF&}「早～今天终于要合格发表了  怎么办～我要紧张了哦～」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智花  原来是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说现在要去看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是个好结果就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想快点让她松口气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沙英学姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是呢  沙英学姐也很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是她的妹妹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「加油！我支持你哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概几点知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是上午
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5F5F5F&}{\3c&FFFFFF&}「谢谢！我会加油的！」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  现在是考试的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情人节  什么巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要兴奋过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  情人节对少女来说是重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说少女之前  先记得你可是教师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那么说的话  我就不给校长巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不回消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也许很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有事的  小智花的话一定没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是张贴在那里的吧  我们的合格发表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我那时真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也松了一大口气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那已经是一年前的事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年收不到巧克力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5F5F5F&}{\3c&FFFFFF&}合格！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟哦  由由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还想分享喜悦的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐不是在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  姐姐也很高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待合格的庆祝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我真的很努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  电车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我这边休息时间也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再说  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小由乃  弘  宫子  沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然人不在  算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  两三张就够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌冬或者荞麦面？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天没有吃面食的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有风  并不怎么感觉冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是便当呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是特意为我们做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无法让小智花吃到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你都不知道结果如何  还…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我相信会合格的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有热茶  也要喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情真舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  热乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小智花发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为纪念拍下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  Double Peace
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我回个消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  小智花不会再来玩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  考试已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次来住一个星期就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些话不要对智花说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她马上就会当真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5F5F5F&}{\3c&FFFFFF&}－发  送－
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5F5F5F&}{\3c&FFFFFF&}－消息已发送－
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃你们这么快就和智花变得要好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小智花是个很和善的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是既开朗又可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是爱吵闹而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是小智花？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说「赤豆饭真好啊  我也想吃」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也发个消息看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「随时都会给你做赤豆饭的  要再来玩哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也要发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道怎么发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MI怎么打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按这个两次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YA是这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里要按5次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体冷吗  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了哦  沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才上屋顶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面分明是大冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在屋顶到底干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是吃了午饭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气晴朗  也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目是在学校食堂吃的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是家里和学校往返的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只要一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  小智花不是一人生活呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她说很想一个人住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呀呀呀  不过一个人住很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一开始尽是些不明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐她们教了我们很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快啊  好差一点点就要一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先搬过来的是小宫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由由的时间很紧凑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我搬过来的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小宫还有弘学姐一起画了兔子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那个吗  还在我家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么穿水手服？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  因为要是不打扫的话  就找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是宫子的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在看来还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好丢脸  我画的是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小孩子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么没有画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐那天是截稿日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  弘学姐  今天的点心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是一直都有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  有什么东西的概率非常高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔了它扔了它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得软绵绵的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软绵绵？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是橘子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  给  吃了它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  之前撒了留下来的豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}{\bord2}注：“节分”日本在立春前一天撒豆子来驱鬼防灾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我再吃自己年纪数量的豆子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}{\bord2}注：日本在节分时要吃豆子，\N一般数量为自己的年龄，也有年龄数+1的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子  手洗干净了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才扫除过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手很干净  房间也变得干净了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然水手服有点脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手服  中学时的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我习惯在打扫的时候穿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美术馆的清扫日的时候也穿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那之后就没有穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为说要穿脏了也没有关系的衣服过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就选了水手服？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其它的了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧的围裙什么的  或者白大褂什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  刚才时间太短  再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我合格了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个刚才不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我不会说那么多次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系  又不会少块肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的只有这些吗  我要挂了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  又变得冷淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  桑原老师要给谁巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不给校长  就觉得他太凄凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会给他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有给校长的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说那样的话  你还给其他人巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给校长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YAHOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是早点去买就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也是刚刚想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  由由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智花说晚饭吃饺子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为是智花最喜欢吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一人份的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是一年份的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好像要胀破的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起出门吗  关系真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能收下吗  我发不完  正伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个广告单已经有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是相同的３张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿5张有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要  请不要随便放进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一个人把这些全部发完吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么冷的天  真辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拿10张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹～吹～吹～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体都冻僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是先进暖炉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先把肉和豆腐放进冰箱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  就放在外面没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温暖～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该要准备了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖烘烘～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家提起干劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  切葱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开切了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小宫  太危险太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用砧板的时候  要把左手弯成像小猫咪的手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猫咪的手？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  我做什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就拜托结一下魔芋丝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我要拿烫的东西过来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置的话这里可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微右边点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  为什么点不上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瓦斯断了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这简直是把我折腾得半死不活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  豆腐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就切到这里了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐真是火锅的幕后主角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这个进去了就真的完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是最后的一道工序了哦  由乃大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我切了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个火锅是算什么火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是鸡肉火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瘦身火锅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  火锅是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  弘姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是大相扑什锦火锅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘姐姐的手制料理真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一碗饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  好会善变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会涨开来的  不可以把饭全部吃完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我是小后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}{\bord2}注：我是小后  在《周刊少年跳跃》上连载的相扑漫画(2003年29号～2004年16号)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始吃纪州面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤还够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系  还剩了许多  剩了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}{\bord2}注：这里的“剩了许多”在相扑中的意思是表示胜负尚未决定的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃热的东西  眼镜果然会起雾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要摘下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是第一次看见沙英学姐把眼睛摘下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为我视力很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这个是什么菜码
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼镜带上  眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘学姐  我们会收拾的  就放在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是在收拾哦  不是还留有点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火锅的最后果然还是火锅小豆汤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去洗澡然后睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和小智花发了很多消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想再和她一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想见面后对她说恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「现在还心情激动得睡不着」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.73,0:22:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}2月6日  结束  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃没有事吧  肌肉痛？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.74,0:23:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是由由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2天才开始痛是年轻的证明哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫不是和我同一年的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个法则说是运动的负担如果大  则会在短时间里痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小的话则会慢慢痛起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.20,0:23:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为和年龄没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘为什么肌肉痛？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.41,0:23:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在半夜里用力踏脚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.41,0:23:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}{\bord2}注：这是相扑的基本准备运动  双脚交替抬高用力踏地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.15,0:24:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFCC0F1&}{\3c&H000084&}不～对！
